  stimulus_text = 'The author of the text is trying to convince the reader that a particular issue is important. The author does this by using a series of rhetorical devices.  These devices include the use of vivid imagery, strong language, and emotional appeals.  The author also uses a lot of repetition to make the reader think about the issue and its consequences.  How does the author’s use of rhetorical devices help to achieve the intended purpose?',
