  stimulus_text = 'The first time I saw her, she was sitting on a park bench, reading a book.  Her long, flowing hair cascaded down her back, and her bright, blue eyes sparkled with intelligence.  She wore a simple, white dress that seemed to glow in the sunlight.  It was a perfect summer day, and the world seemed to be at peace. Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
